{"tid":1845154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"邊條仆街係醫院放炸彈","createTime":"2020-01-27T03:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T02:20:34.000Z","uid":27530,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"48aa72342d2e9db0bfd563bc3d58fa60f8eb7b8c","tid":1845154,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c7003b6ac25debdd3d76c2e69f5b72150fde9a","tid":1845154,"uid":242427,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:03:41.000Z","msg":"真係嫌醫院班職員唔夠忙, 仲可能有老人家或者細路哥會用廁所, 呢啲人真係好過份"},{"pid":"6fbb68ddc91c3fad186cdde745044c982fc315fa","tid":1845154,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"（取笑系列）抗爭者真係好垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844940</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"187975712490bcb31b44c10ca7ffa8e4ee669ba5","tid":1845154,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"咩料?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16af941eeb848fa7805ee7cdd60d573abd09e3c7","tid":1845154,"uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"凌晨2時許，長沙灣明愛醫院懷信樓近急症室一個男廁發生火警，約20名於急症室候診的人需疏散，消防趕至時火種已熄滅，事件中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n大批防暴警到場封鎖急症室一帶調查，爆炸品處理課於廁所內發現懷疑爆炸品碎片，交由重案組接手跟進，至凌晨5時許急症室重開。<br />\n<br />\n深水埗警區刑事總督察莊翹偉表示，事發時急症室男廁曾傳出兩下爆炸聲，冒出火光及大量白煙，警方首先到場，協助20名於急症室候診的人疏散，同時將火救熄。<br />\n<br />\n莊翹偉稱涉事男廁其中一個廁格的馬桶損毁碎裂，爆炸品處理課到場時，於馬桶後方下發現一個約闊10厘米、高15厘米的玻璃器皿，器皿內檢獲電線及電池，懷疑是一個威力不大的自製炸彈，相信炸彈內藏粉狀爆炸物，暫未確定引爆方法及殺傷力等，案件交由深水埗警區重案組接手調查。"},{"pid":"0e9497a91a81e8e1e73803d589fd11dab932e7ff","tid":1845154,"uid":316048,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">爆左自己區個醫院就唔洗收疫病人? 識玩噢</span></span>"},{"pid":"f88d97197e065e08c9c1adfaee9bccea5f70599c","tid":1845154,"uid":112622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:09:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af044c075bcaf4588a9ee4a2a5756d3db6336d40","tid":1845154,"uid":277186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:10:00.000Z","msg":"會唔會係支那病人原地爆炸 支爆？"},{"pid":"d0dbbe7af215e937e7eee980420caf9b6365d6d6","tid":1845154,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0e9497a91a81e8e1e73803d589fd11dab932e7ff","tid":1845154,"uid":316048,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">爆左自己區個醫院就唔洗收疫病人? 識玩噢</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:12:43.000Z","msg":"67菠蘿會？"},{"pid":"5d0dc9cce36bdf0b0673791db59642e3f2b43b09","tid":1845154,"uid":265179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:13:31.000Z","msg":"凡係罷工/遊行之前次次都發現炸彈"},{"pid":"ccfdd1de8fdc35e1a20a55bab9a3242daf2414b1","tid":1845154,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾有炸彈都唔好係醫院放啦&hellip;"},{"pid":"fc451df5077e445c7aca916b5d6f1c8de163eb8b","tid":1845154,"uid":28432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:14:25.000Z","msg":"呢排成日罵黑醫黑護既係咩人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1526caa497868cfbc7988fd681a04d0eed66a1e0","tid":1845154,"uid":212897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"一定係便衣警搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7431066dc53c078d7a8db7c29779127813c87d0c","tid":1845154,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc451df5077e445c7aca916b5d6f1c8